text: Tom Fawcett (born 18 October 1995) is an American tennis player. Fawcett has a career high ATP singles ranking of 400 achieved on 7 January 2019. He also has a career high ATP doubles ranking of 602 achieved on 15 July 2019. Fawcett made his Grand Slam main draw debut at the 2018 US Open after receiving a wildcard into the qualifying singles draw, and mixed doubles main draw with Danielle Collins. ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:American male tennis players Category:People from Winnetka, Illinois Category:People from Skokie, Illinois Category:Stanford Cardinal men's tennis players Category:Tennis people from Illinois
